column16: Eduardo Escobar grounds out, pitcher Carlos Ruiz to first baseman Danny Valencia.
Kennys Vargas called out on strikes.
Robbie Grossman pops out to second baseman Robinson Cano.
Umpire reviewed (home run), call on the field was upheld: Chris Gimenez doubles (4) on a fly ball to left fielder Ben Gamel.   Ehire Adrianza to 3rd.
Eddie Rosario homers (8) on a fly ball to right center field.
